secondary_outcome.description:
To compare corneal nerve density (CND) between
children with T1D for 5 years or more to children without diabetes;
children with T1D with and without evidence of DN;
to examine the relationship between CND, CNL & CBD and known risk factors of DN

To compare corneal nerve length (CNL), by CCM between
children with T1D for 5 years or more to children without diabetes;
children with T1D with and without evidence of DN;
to examine the relationship between CND, CNL & CBD and known risk factors of DN

To compare corneal nerve branching density (CBD) by CCM between
children with T1D for 5 years or more to children without diabetes;
children with T1D with and without evidence of DN;
to examine the relationship between CND, CNL & CBD and known risk factors of DN
